%p
  - if current_user && current_user.registrations_for_event(event).present?
    Click #{link_to "here", attendance_status_path(current_user.registrations_for_event(event).first)} to check the status of your registration to #{event.name}.
    %br
    If you wish to add another registration for someone else, fill the form #{link_to "here", new_event_attendance_path(event)}.
  - else
    Click #{link_to "here", new_event_attendance_path(event)} to register for #{event.name}.
